thread.title: Bill Gross: Fed will hike rates in Sept as financial conditions a priority
thread.title_full: Bill Gross: Fed will hike rates in Sept as financial conditions a priority | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Bill Gross: Fed will hike rates in Sept as financial conditions a priority
text:
Aug 19 Bond investing guru Bill Gross of Janus Capital Group Inc said in a tweet on Wednesday that the U.S. Federal Reserve will hike rates in September as financial market conditions take precedence over economic conditions.
"Rate hike in Sept. Financial conditions not economic conditions a priority. That means they begin to normalize despite data," Gross said. (Reporting by Jennifer Ablan in New York; Editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)
